                                        <p>Child plans are a combination of investment and insurance that help in financial planning for your child's future needs. As a parent you can secure your childâ€™s future with plans that include children insurance plans and children education plans. A child plan ensures payment of a lump-sum amount to a child on maturity to cover higher education or marriage expenses</p>
