                                        <p class="blue-text font-medium">Accidental Coverage</p>
                                        <p class="mb-8">If your bike meets with an accident, you can simply claim insurance against the repair expenses without bearing the load on your own pocket.</p>

                                        <p class="blue-text font-medium">Third Party Liability</p>
                                        <p>In case of an accident, the insurance policy will provide cover to reimburse damages to the third partyâ€™s vehicle or property. Additionally, medical expenses incurred for treatment or hospitalisation expenses are also taken care of.</p>

                                        <p class="blue-tex">Safety Against Natural Disasters</p>
                                        <p class="mb-8">If your bike is damaged due to flood, fire or earthquake, your comprehensive bike insurance policy will cover for the damages.</p>

                                        <p class="blue-text font-medium">Cover Against Theft and Vandalism</p>
                                        <p class="mb-8">Comprehensive bike insurance provides you cover against theft and vandalism. You can get your hard-earned money back if your car gets stolen.</p>

                                        <p class="blue-text font-medium">No Claim Bonus</p>
                                        <p>In case no loss arises, you get rewarded a No Claim Bonus (NCB) for not filing any bike insurance claim that year. This makes your insurance renewal premium cheaper.</p>

                                    </div>
                                    
                                    
