                                    <!-- #Add-On and Covers -->
                                    <div id="add-on" class="py-12">
                                        <h2 class="heading-tertiary">Add-On Covers</h2>
                                        <p class="mb-4">Add-on is an additional benefit added to your car policy which covers the car against unforeseen expenses. Add-ons, also known as riders, can be included in your insurance policy by paying extra premium.</p>
                                        
