                                        </h2>
                                        <ul class="list-disc leading-loose ml-12">
                                            <li>Normal wear and tear of the vehicle.</li>
                                            <li>Not having a valid driving license during an accident</li>
                                            <li>Driving under the influence of intoxicating liquor/ drugs</li>
                                            <li>Accident taking place beyond geographical limits</li>
                                            <li>Electrical or mechanical breakdown</li>
                                            <li>If the vehicle is being used for unlawful purposes</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
