                                            <li><strong>Passengers Carrying Commercial Vehicle:</strong> Vehicles that are used to transport passengers from one place to the other with the intention of earning a livelihood, for eg, a bus, auto-rickshaws, taxi, cabs, etc. fall under the category of passenger carrying vehicle.</li>
                                            <li><strong>Heavy Commercial Vehicle:</strong>  Vehicles used for construction, mining, loading of heavy goods for example truck; crane, etc fall under the category of heavy vehicles. They have higher liabilities than other commercial vehicles.</li>
